<plot>A girl, leaning against the wall, seems to wait for someone. Julien/Pierrot, leaving a movie theatre, wanders around a hardly recognizable Bologna. Between life and film, walking through visual spaces and soundscapes, the characters touch, lose, find again, and chase each other, making indistinguishable bodies and ghosts.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425263</url></doc>
